    {
        "user": "UC2A2ARPT",
        "type": "message",
        "ts": "1769183119.582659",
        "client_msg_id": "443A769D-5181-47AE-AEB8-86DC6FB8B0DB",
        "text": "The \"another world\" vs \"merged with our everyday world\" is a fantastic point (pun… sure).\n\nI can certainly recognize in my own life how the gradual encroach of computer magic into ever more facets of daily life was initially exciting and then disheartening as the technology became less and less about personal empowerment.\n\nI'd happy give up most of the internet to go back to an era where the computer was a bounded space.",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
